---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout title="Terms of Service | SelectStream Shop">
  <article class="legal-page">
    <h1>Terms of Service</h1>
    <p class="last-updated">Last Updated: April 9, 2026</p>

    <section>
      <h2>1. Curation Authority</h2>
      <p>SelectStream Shop provides high-signal curation of creator gear. While we strive for 100% data accuracy, product specifications and prices are subject to change by the original manufacturers or retailers.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>2. Use of the Stream</h2>
      <p>Users are permitted to use the "Setup Builder" for personal curation and discovery. Any automated scraping of the SelectStream signal database is strictly prohibited.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>3. External Links & Affiliates</h2>
      <p>Our stream contains links to external retailers (including Amazon). We are not responsible for the fulfillment, shipping, or support of products purchased through these external links.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>4. Visual Property</h2>
      <p>The "Matte Black" visual silhouettes and high-contrast branding elements on this site are the intellectual property of SelectStream.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>5. Termination</h2>
      <p>We reserve the right to modify or terminate the stream at any time to maintain our high-signal standards.</p>
    </section>
  </article>
</MainLayout>

<style>
  .legal-page {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 8rem auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #999;
  }

  h1 { font-size: 3rem; color: #fff; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  h2 { font-size: 1.2rem; color: #fff; margin-top: 3rem; letter-spacing: 0.1rem; }
  .last-updated { font-size: 0.7rem; color: #444; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.2rem; margin-bottom: 4rem; }
  section { margin-bottom: 2rem; }
</style>
